地），我爱人百般恳求没好使，六个月后才回来，导致我爱人孕初期基本天天哭，甚至产生了轻生念头。 ⑤我家的事基本没有参与过，但经常指手画脚，干涉我家事情。 此事，我知道矛盾爆发事的做法不妥，将我爱人夹到中间，目前我能感到我爱人情绪不太好，因此恳请各位帮着想个办法。感谢各位。"},"attached_info":"Cj8ItuyTxNLf7JtAEAMaCTEwOTQxOTIyOCCunO+0BjAAOEhACHIJNjYyMTM2MTE2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"87 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"9_1721805580.409811","card_id":"Q_662362770","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":662362770,"title":"喜欢健身的人每天下班后要花精力去健身、饮食要控制，感觉活得很累，这种生活有何意义？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/662362770","type":"question","created":1721713913,"answer_count":54,"follower_count":80,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[658,833,974,3776,3603458],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8ItuyTxNLf7JtAEAMaCTEwOTQ2OTQ4NSD5if20BjAAOFBACXIJNjYyMzYyNzcweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"85 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-44305c056b5f3a0a3ef99223372d73dc_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"10_1721805580.410141","card_id":"Q_662180757","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":662180757,"title":"《原神》4.8 版本剧情做完的玩家聊聊感受怎么样？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/662180757","type":"question","created":1721539726,"answer_count":109,"follower_count":106,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bo